---
tags: [ hardware ]
---
# Outputs the device tree showing hardware paths
lshw -short

# Outputs the device tree as an HTML page
lshw -html > device-info.html # Open it by IE

# Only show the given class of hardware.
# class can be found using 'lshw -short' or 'lshw -businfo'.
lshw -class network # 显示网络相关设备信息

